data.name: xGrid1.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.NAEWON_DATE , ( CASE WHEN LENGTH( A.JUBSU_TIME ) = 4 THEN SUBSTR(A.JUBSU_TIME, 1, 2)||':'||SUBSTR(A.JUBSU_TIME, 3) ELSE '' END ) JINRYO_PRE_TIME, FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME (A.GWA , A.NAEWON_DATE) GWA_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.NAEWON_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME, A.PKOUT1001 PKOUT1001, NVL(A.NAEWON_YN, 'N') NAEWON_YN, A.BUNHO BUNHO, A.GWA GWA, A.DOCTOR DOCTOR, DECODE(A.NAEWON_TYPE, '1', 'Y', 'N') JINRYO_IRAI_YN, A.SYS_DATE IRAI_DATE, A.RES_CHANGGU RES_USER, B.COMMENTS RESER_COMMENT, B.RESER_GUBUN RESER_GUBUN FROM OUT1001 A , OUT0123 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.RESER_YN = 'Y' AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.BUNHO(+) = A.BUNHO AND A.NAEWON_DATE >= TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND B.COMMENT_TYPE(+) = '1' AND B.FKOUT1001(+) = A.PKOUT1001 AND B.SEQ(+) = '1' ORDER BY A.NAEWON_DATE, A.JUBSU_TIME
